## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ibrutinib Imbruvica 2014** = first FDA covalent BTK inhibitor CLL — paradigm shift from chemoimmunotherapy. C481 covalent binding + irreversible. RESONATE + RESONATE-2 + ECOG-1912 superiority over FCR/BR. quantum-VQE 의 covalent BTK pocket fit.
2. **pirtobrutinib Jaypirca 2023** = first FDA non-covalent BTK inhibitor R/R CLL post-covalent. C481S resistance escape + reversible non-covalent paradigm. BRUIN trial. quantum-VQE 의 non-covalent allosteric-adjacent pocket leverage.
3. **venetoclax Venclexta 2016** = first FDA BCL-2 selective inhibitor CLL — paradigm shift. BH3-mimetic + minimal residual disease (MRD)-negative complete response. CLL14 (venetoclax + obinutuzumab 1L) + MURANO (venetoclax + rituximab R/R) + GLOW (venetoclax + ibrutinib 1L). quantum-VQE 의 BCL-2 BH3 pocket fit.
4. **acalabrutinib + zanubrutinib 2017+2019/2023** = second/third-gen BTK selective — 만성 atrial fibrillation/bleeding 부작용 reduction. ELEVATE-RR + ALPINE head-to-head superiority over ibrutinib. quantum-VQE 의 selectivity profile differential.
5. **idelalisib 2014 + duvelisib 2018 + umbralisib 2021 (withdrawn 2022)** = PI3Kδ class — 만성 hepatotox/colitis/pneumonitis class-effect 부작용. CLL/SLL 임상 위치 한정. umbralisib 2022 withdrawal = class-wide regulatory caution signal.
6. **lisocabtagene maraleucel Breyanzi 2024 R/R CLL/SLL** = first FDA CD19 CAR-T CLL. TRANSCEND CLL 004 — post-BTK + post-BCL-2 R/R. CRS/ICANS 부작용 + manufacturing turnaround. liso-cel + ibrutinib combo 임상.
7. **obinutuzumab Gazyva 2013/2014 CLL** = second-gen glycoengineered anti-CD20 — afucosylated Fc enhanced ADCC. CLL11 (obinutuzumab + chlorambucil > rituximab + chlorambucil). CLL14 1L venetoclax + obinutuzumab fixed-duration paradigm.
8. **FCR (fludarabine + cyclophosphamide + rituximab) historical 1L** = IGHV-mutated 만성 CLL 임상 historical 표준 — 11+ year follow-up MRD-negative subset cure-like. BTK + BCL-2 era 후 chemoimmunotherapy 임상 위치 한정.
9. **17p del / TP53 / IGHV-unmutated high-risk stratification** = chemoimmunotherapy 부적합 + targeted (BTK/BCL-2) preferred. ibrutinib + acalabrutinib + zanubrutinib + venetoclax 가 17p del 1L 표준.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, CLL/SLL 임상 의미 한정. K-CLL + 식약처 framework cross-link.

